Write a screenshot tool, using
- scrot source code
	https://github.com/resurrecting-open-source-projects/scrot
	https://github.com/dreamer/scrot/blob/master/src/main.c
- xscreenshot https://git.2f30.org/xscreenshot/file/xscreenshot.c.html
Some useful features:
- full screen
- click to capture a window
- drag to capture a region
- click two points to select a region
- add a delay

